The paper deals with the problem of knowledge compilation, which is a fundamental problem in artificial intelligence (AI) and logic (LO). It also involves the use of data structures (DS) and algorithms for combining them (DM). The paper also discusses the complexity of the Apply function, which is a topic in computational complexity (CC). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI and cs.LO, followed by cs.DS, cs.DM, and cs.CC.
